file.name: path_param.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: PayloadV
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/payloadV"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /locations/{id}/rooms:
    get:
      summary: Reperesents Snowpeak room collection resource
      operationId: getLocationsIdRooms
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: Unique identification of location
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
components: {}
